InventoryItems.Name: Lego Racers Storming Enforcer
InventoryItems.Description:
Send the other racers running from the Storming Enforcer!
Load the 3-wheeled police bike onto the air stomper and get ready to burn rubber! Stomp on the pump and watch the Storming Enforcer take off like a hurricane! Give it your best stomp action!
•Features cool racing details including an extra wide front wheel, powerful jet engine and bulldog logo •Storming Enforcer measures 6” (17cm) long, 2” (6cm) high and 3” (8cm) wide •Stomp the pump for real racing action!
